data.description: Discover your ideal Boise retreat! This 3 bed, 2 bath gem boasts a built-in dog run and sits across from Cypress Park with incredible foothill views. Enjoy brand new landscaping, a bonus office, and a spacious 3-car garage with built-in storage, workbenches and great lighting. Live moments from outdoor adventures and downtown delights. Schedule your showing today!
